{"tid":627843,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每個人都有存在嘅定位","createTime":"2018-04-13T10:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T10:28:16.000Z","uid":134484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a0c8052eeb3b924fcf4869c4704ab3b7ed12574","tid":627843,"uid":134484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"有人生而為皇<br />\n有人生而為奴<br />\n有人生而成神<br />\n有人生而成魔<br />\n每個人喺世界都有定位<br />\n有啲人有做皇者嘅資質<br />\n注定幹一番事業登頂<br />\n有啲人甘於平淡<br />\n唔好唔衰 唔勁唔廢<br />\n平平安安渡過一生就係最好嘅結果<br />\n有啲人自甘墮落<br />\n注定做社會嘅地底泥<br />\n然後怨天怨地<br />\n神仙都救唔返<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bb17458285a02b07b944ff75ce2ae95c8db7dc","tid":627843,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"最尾果幾句咪連登班公屋仔既寫照囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e85827cfb1b9b94a3b7e324fe683fb896c2dfa4","tid":627843,"uid":134484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44002fddbaefd344450d4736e7f256e04b5f36f3","tid":627843,"uid":134484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06bb17458285a02b07b944ff75ce2ae95c8db7dc","tid":627843,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"最尾果幾句咪連登班公屋仔既寫照囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}